    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have been cooking for 25 min, move them to one side and add the <strong>sliced bread roll</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s]</p><p>Top the <strong>bread roll base[s]</strong> with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for a final 5 min or until the bread roll is crusty and the cheese has melted</p>",
